    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">The Bakuton clan has a unique talent for manifesting Explosion Release due to their close affinity to both Earth and Lightning Release. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">Beginning at 7th level you gain the second Nature release you didn't select from Explosion Release Affinity clan trait and when casting a Bakuton Clan Hijutsu or Ninjutsu with the Earth or Lightning release keywords, you can change the damage type if any to force and increase the size of the area of effect by +15ft, if it has one.</span></p>",
